engines.customers: SELECT CUSTOMER, COUNT(*) AS TOTAL FROM DASH14467.BLADE_DAMAGE GROUP BY CUSTOMER
engines.damage_per_flight: SELECT FLIGHT_ID, SUM(DAMAGE) AS TOTAL_DAMAGE FROM DASH14467.BLADE_DAMAGE GROUP BY FLIGHT_ID
engines.core_speed: SELECT CUSTOMER, FLIGHT_ID, FAILED, CORE_SPEED FROM DASH14467.BLADE_DAMAGE WHERE ENGINE_TYPEB=2 ORDER BY CORE_SPEED DESC FETCH FIRST 100 ROW ONLY

prosa.comercios: SELECT COMERCIO FROM DASH14467.PROSA GROUP BY COMERCIO
prosa.comercios_importe_promedio: SELECT COMERCIO, AVG(IMPORTE) AS IMPORTE_PROMEDIO FROM DASH14467.PROSA GROUP BY COMERCIO
prosa.comercios_resumen: SELECT COMERCIO, AVG(IMPORTE) AS IMPORTE_PROMEDIO, SUM(IMPORTE) AS IMPORTE_TOTAL FROM DASH14467.PROSA GROUP BY COMERCIO
prosa.comercios_top_ten: SELECT COMERCIO, AVG(IMPORTE) AS IMPORTE_PROMEDIO, SUM(IMPORTE) AS IMPORTE_TOTAL FROM DASH14467.PROSA GROUP BY COMERCIO ORDER BY IMPORTE_TOTAL DESC FETCH FIRST 10 ROW ONLY
